lenders.name: The Doyle Family
lenders.loan_because: Our family lives in the United States, where we have the opportunity to  borrow money, combine it with a dream and hard work, and create a better future for ourselves. We realize that in other parts of the world, money is not always available to borrow so easily, if at all. Through Kiva.org, we are able to extend financial opportunity to people and places where it is most needed. We are happy to believe that a family far away from us - and one that we would never meet or affect otherwise - is living a better life with our help.
